    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Straw from the barley plant, traditionally used in Europe and Asia as braided plaits for hats. In the Americas, it was used as a packing material, particularly for shipping glass. It is also used as an animal feed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
